From 00ae15f5a798973067fe5a952cc67aa9bdd8c3fd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Thu, 11 Dec 2025 23:00:09 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 52/73] arm64: dts: cix: Update GPU node to match vendor
 Panthor config

Update the Sky1 GPU device tree node to match the vendor kernel
configuration for compatibility with mainline Panthor driver.

Changes:
- Use arm,mali-valhall compatible (vendor DT compatible)
- Reorder reg to put RCSU first (resource 0), GPU second (resource 1)
- Update clock-names to use vendor naming (gpu_clk_core, gpu_clk_stacks)
- Update panthor driver to accept both vendor and mainline clock names
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1.dtsi            |  19 ++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/cix/linlon-dp/linlondp_kms.c |   4 +-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_devfreq.c    |  16 ++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_device.c     | 123 +++++++++++++++++--
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_device.h     |   9 ++
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_fw.c         |  10 +-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_gpu.c        |  10 +-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_mmu.c        |  10 +-
 8 files changed, 165 insertions(+), 36 deletions(-)

